OL,3,CLorry crashes into coffee shop
OL,4,Cinjuring one
OL,6,FA lorry crashed into a coffee shop in
OL,7,Fthe early hours of Saturday morning,
OL,8,Finjuring a person and causing severe
OL,9,Fdamage to the building.
OL,11,FEast Sussex Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,Fsaid it was called to the shop on the
OL,13,FA22 in Nutley at 03:30 this morning.
OL,15,FA Fire Service spokesperson said one
OL,16,Fperson was treated for minor injuries
OL,17,Fby an ambulance crew.
