OL,3,CLorry crashes into coffee shop
OL,4,Cinjuring one
OL,6,FThey went on to say "Everyone from the
OL,7,Fproperty was safe and no-one was
OL,8,Ftrapped in the vehicle. The road has
OL,9,Fbeen closed while emergency services
OL,10,Fremove the lorry and make the building
OL,11,Fsafe."
OL,13,FThe fire service urged people to avoid
OL,14,Fthe area and said it had requested UK
OL,15,FPower Networks to attend as cables
OL,16,Fhave been damaged.
